Package de.akquinet.jbosscc.guttenbase.export.zip

Interface Summary
ZipConstants Commonly used constants.
ZipExporterClassResources When exporting to e JAR/ZIP file we allow to add custom classes and resources to the resultiung JAR.
 

Class Summary
ZipAbstractMetaDataWriter Base implementation the gathers all properties and stores them into a file of the ZIP.
ZipClassesFromClassResourceExporter Copy all classes and data that can be found relative to the given class resource to the generated JAR/ZIP.
ZipColumnMetaDataWriter Write ZIP file entry containing information about a table column such as type and name.
ZipDatabaseMetaDataWriter Write ZIP file entry containing information about data base such as schema or version.
ZipExporter Export schema information and data into executable JAR file.
ZipImporter Read database information and data from ZIP file.
ZipIndexMetaDataWriter Write ZIP file entry containing information about a table column index such as name and columns.
ZipStartup Default tool to start when "executing" the JAR file.
ZipTableMetaDataWriter Write ZIP file entry containing information about a table such as name and row count.
